import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LogoContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing.sm};
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: ${props => props.theme.transitions.base};
  
  &:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
`;

const LogoIcon = styled.div`
  width: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  height: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
`;

const LogoText = styled.span`
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.fonts.primary};
  font-weight: ${props => props.theme.fontWeights.bold};
  font-size: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? props.theme.fontSizes['2xl'] : 
                        props.size === 'medium' ? props.theme.fontSizes.xl : 
                        props.theme.fontSizes.lg};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.gradientPrimary};
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
`;

const LokanexLogo = ({ size = 'medium', showText = true, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <LogoContainer {...props}>
      <LogoIcon size={size}>
        <svg
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          viewBox="0 0 100 100"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          {/* Background blur effect */}
          <circle
            cx="50"
            cy="50"
            r="45"
            fill="url(#bgBlur)"
            opacity="0.4"
          />
          
          {/* Glassmorphism container */}
          <rect
            x="20"
            y="20"
            width="60"
            height="60"
            rx="15"
            fill="url(#glassFill)"
            stroke="url(#glassStroke)"
            strokeWidth="1"
            opacity="0.8"
          />
          
          {/* Modern L with cut corner */}
          <path
            d="M30 30 L30 70 L60 70 L60 50 L50 50 L50 30 Z"
            fill="url(#lGradient)"
            stroke="url(#lStroke)"
            strokeWidth="0.5"
          />
          
          {/* Floating orbs */}
          <circle cx="75" cy="25" r="4" fill="url(#orb1)" opacity="0.8" />
          <circle cx="25" cy="75" r="3" fill="url(#orb2)" opacity="0.7" />
          <circle cx="80" cy="70" r="2.5" fill="url(#orb3)" opacity="0.6" />
          
          {/* Gradient lines */}
          <line x1="30" y1="30" x2="75" y2="25" stroke="url(#line1)" strokeWidth="2" opacity="0.5" />
          <line x1="60" y1="70" x2="25" y2="75" stroke="url(#line2)" strokeWidth="2" opacity="0.5" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="80" y2="70" stroke="url(#line3)" strokeWidth="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          
          {/* Neon glow effect */}
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="25" fill="url(#neonGlow)" opacity="0.3" />
          
          {/* Micro dots pattern */}
          <circle cx="15" cy="15" r="1" fill="url(#dot1)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="85" cy="15" r="1" fill="url(#dot2)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="15" cy="85" r="1" fill="url(#dot3)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="85" cy="85" r="1" fill="url(#dot4)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="10" r="1" fill="url(#dot5)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="90" r="1" fill="url(#dot6)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="10" cy="50" r="1" fill="url(#dot7)" opacity="0.6" />
          <circle cx="90" cy="50" r="1" fill="url(#dot8)" opacity="0.6" />
          
          {/* Gradients */}
          <defs>
            <radialGradient id="bgBlur" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.3" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" stopOpacity="0.2" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" stopOpacity="0.1" />
            </radialGradient>
            <linearGradient id="glassFill" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="rgba(0,212,255,0.05)" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="rgba(78,205,196,0.1)" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="glassStroke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="rgba(0,212,255,0.2)" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="lGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="25%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="75%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="lStroke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="orb1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="orb2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="orb3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <linearGradient id="line1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="line2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="line3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="neonGlow" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.4" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" stopOpacity="0.2" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" stopOpacity="0.1" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot4" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot5" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot6" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot7" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="dot8" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </LogoIcon>
      {showText && <LogoText size={size}>Lokanex</LogoText>}
    </LogoContainer>
  );
};

export default LokanexLogo;
